## Key Insights

### 1. Fintech Dominance
Fintech consistently led unicorn creation across all three years,
peaking sharply in 2021.

### 2. 2021 Growth Surge
All top industries experienced significant growth in 2021,
indicating strong post-pandemic investor confidence.

### 3. Valuation Trend
Although 2019 had fewer unicorns, average valuations were higher,
suggesting more conservative but high-value investments.

### 4. Internet Software Stability
Internet software & services maintained steady unicorn creation,
highlighting its long-term scalability.
